video.title: Hello, My Twenties!
video.synopsis: With different personalities, life goals and taste in men, five female college students become housemates in a shared residence called Belle Epoque.

episodes.synopsis: The last of five to join the Belle Epoque shared residence, timid Eun-jae arrives in Seoul. She finds her housemates just as cold as the city itself.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: House rules say men are forbidden to enter, but Ye-eun discovers men's underwear in their home. Conscience-stricken, she decides to hide it.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: After discovering I-na's secret, Ye-eun declares that she cannot live in the same house as I-na. Meanwhile, I-na encounters a strange man at a bar.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: On top of school, Jin-myung works day and night to sustain herself. She has no time for romance, but a guy from work keeps dropping hints.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: In an effort to chase away the ghost in their house, the ladies of Belle Epoque decide to bring men in -- by hosting a house party.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: The party isn't a huge success, but the housemates still make it memorable while uncovering some secrets but also leaving many questions unanswered.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Money has always been a problem for Jin-myung, but when a promising job offer drops into her lap, she faces a difficult situation.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: There seems to be a suspicious man lurking around Belle Epoque at night, and each of the housemates has a guess as to who it could be.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: While her mom is out of the country on vacation, Eun-jae learns some disconcerting news involving her family members.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: When a few of the housemates make some drastic life decisions, Ji-won is worried that it's all because of the lie she fabricated.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: With Ye-eun missing, Jin-myung's mom in a legal mess and Eun-jae awaiting the autopsy results, Belle Epoque is just riddled with problems.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: As the Belle Epoque housemates discover, some things are better left unsaid, some people never change and some problems just never get solved.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Jin-myung gets excited when she finds her housemates waiting to pick her up from the airport, but for some reason, they don't seem happy to see her.
episodes.title: Angry Over Small Things #TheWorldofUs

episodes.synopsis: With their landlady pressing them to pick a new housemate soon, the Belle Epoque quartet has no other choice but to lower their standards ... a lot.
episodes.title: Coward #TheStranger

episodes.synopsis: As Eun-jae and Ye-eun try to cope with the stresses of a new semester, Ji-won is still her usual perky self, but something keeps troubling her.
episodes.title: Decide to Hate #CrimeandPunishment

episodes.synopsis: Returning home and finding a strange man in their bathroom, Ji-won, Ye-eun and Eun-jae panic, but it's Jo Eun who seems especially traumatized.
episodes.title: To Survive #TheSelfishGene

episodes.synopsis: As Jo Eun struggles to define her friendship with Ye-ji, Eun-jae frantically searches for a way to undo the message she sent to Jong-yeol by accident.
episodes.title: Wavering Heart #FirstLove

episodes.synopsis: Ye-eun teaches the housemates tricks to win over guys' hearts, which Ji-won uses on Sung-min to make him join her quest to recover her lost memories.
episodes.title: I'm a Miracle #InSearchofLostTime

episodes.synopsis: Suspecting Kwon Ho-chang to be the sender of the unpleasant text message, Ye-eun enlists Ji-won's help in figuring out what kind of person he is.
episodes.title: Center of the World #TheScarletLetter

episodes.synopsis: After hearing the alarming news about Ye-eun's ex-boyfriend from her lawyer, the housemates remind one another to be extra careful from now on.
episodes.title: Self-Dishonesty #Confessions

episodes.synopsis: Ye-eun is certain the letter is meant for her. Ji-won, Eun-jae and Jo Eun visit the bookstore to find the owner of the book that contained the letter.
episodes.title: Wounds #ParadiseLost

episodes.synopsis: As the housemates fail to console Ye-eun, help comes from I-na, who makes a surprise visit. I-na also sheds light on where the pink letter is from.
episodes.title: Might Be Me #TheSenseofanEnding

episodes.synopsis: The unidentified assailant demands to know why the housemates came looking for "Joanne" and provides a crucial piece of information about the letter.
episodes.title: Betraying Oneself #Disgrace

episodes.synopsis: Using Ji-won as an excuse, Jin-myung convinces the housemates to go apple picking. But in fact, everyone -- not just Ji-won -- needs a little break.
episodes.title: Affirming Oneself #StandbyMe

episodes.synopsis: The housemates surprise Eun-jae with a small party when she returns from meeting with Jong-yeol. Ji-won visits her elementary school art teacher.
episodes.title: Seeing Oneself #AllthePrettyHorses

episodes.synopsis: All the pieces of Ji-won's childhood memory finally come together. Meanwhile, Jin-myung stresses over keeping the "promise" she made to Heimdal.
episodes.title: Their Mirrors #SoLongSeeYouTomorrow
